data.description: Take advantage of an assumable mortgage with a low interest rate or get your own | Exquisite 2021-built Silverado Ranch gem! This discriminating one-story residence boasts a Semi-fenced yard, a three-car garage, and a great curb appeal. With low HOA fees, the four bedrooms and three baths, coupled with a bonus room, ensure ample space for comfortable living. The in-law suite adds an extra layer of versatility, catering to various family needs. Ideally located just minutes from shopping and entertainment, this meticulously maintained property showcases a commitment to quality accentuated by numerous design upgrades. Seize the opportunity to indulge in a blend of luxury and practicality.  House features: High ceilings, Granite countertops, Under-sink Reverse Osmosis, Smart blinds, Covered lanai.
